
    AN AUSTRALIAN woman got a Christmas surprise of a
different kind when she discovered a dangerous snake resting on her flip flops.According to Sunshine Coast Daily, the unnamed woman from
Caloundra on Australia’s east coast got the fright of her life on Christmas eve when she spotted
a juvenile Red-bellied Black Snake coiled on top of her flip flops. The venom
of this kind of snake can be deadly, although it is not always fatal.A photo of the shocking discovery was posted on the
